    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287960/extras/b9a98447b959d36b1b4b58878d8218a8.avif?t=1749385157\" width=616 height=72 /></span>自从金发修女索菲晋升为驱魔修女的第一天起，她就被她所信仰的神明刻下了代表祝福的印记，并且注定会在不久之后的将来成为几百年以来的第一任圣女。但要成为圣女绝非易事——因为她必须前往各处已经被魔物占据的圣地，消灭那里的邪恶存在，宣扬神明的威能。她的冒险之旅能否一帆风顺？这一切都要交给屏幕前的您来决定！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287960/extras/bc12ccd72b92f5c3a93a0279d963c2e9.avif?t=1749385157\" width=616 height=72 /></span>动作类RPG游戏</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这部动作类RPG作品当中，您的任务是使用不同的策略对抗不同类型的敌人们，掌握它们的攻击时机与策略，合理规划各种能力值，对拦路的强敌们迎头痛击！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287960/extras/9b5bd9aedf16538de4939ba703d80d0f.avif?t=1749385157\" width=616 height=72 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287960/extras/7a486b0954bb0a62bb3696f6e6867633.avif?t=1749385157\" width=616 height=399 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287960/extras/5868177bebb5d3cdaf82f60fc5773ed1.avif?t=1749385157\" width=616 height=399 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2287960/extras/3906cc3d20e2b3a562cb550a150b8ca0.avif?t=1749385157\" width=616 height=399 /></span></p>",
